items.name: On-Chain-Snake-
items.description: "On-Chain Snake" is a decentralized version of the classic Snake game running on the Ethereum blockchain. Players control the snake by sending transactions, collect food, and compete for the highest score.  Every move is recorded on-chain, and the highest score is stored in the smart contract.

items.description: Gérez des tâches en temps réel avec notifications instantanées via WebSockets. Fonctionnalités : CRUD des tâches, gestion des statuts, authentification JWT, et dashboard statistique. Idéal pour to-do lists et gestion de projets.
